{"id":"shepham","term":"Shepham","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>A treeless place, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 34:10\">Num. 34:10</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 34:11\">11</a>: “The coast shall go down from Shepham to Riblah.”</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Numbers 34:10","Numbers 34:11"]}